            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>... which God your Lord gave you. Do not murder. Do not commit adultery. Do not
                    steal. ...</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>The Deuteronomy version of the Ten Commandments contains a command to put the
                    words upon doors, so Samaritans include the Ten Commandments in the Mezuzahs on
                    their doorways.</p>
            </div>
